oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Country Music Month plug - Joey Bishop Show - 1970-10
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Excerpt from the Joey Bishop show, in which Molly Bee (performer) presents Joey Bishop (host) with a 10 gallon hat, on behalf of Chris Lane, with radio station WJJD, in exchange for a Country Music Month plug, in the October of 1970.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Opening theme -- Opening statement ([Unidentified]) -- [Unidentified] introduces Joey Bishop -- Joey Bishop talks and jokes with the audience -- Joey Bishop introduces Molly Bee -- Molly Bee presents Bishop with a 10 gallon hat on behalf of Chris Lane from WJJD -- Joey Bishop thanks Molly Bee for the gift -- Bishop jokes with the audience (incomplete)
